# Whitelist for lint-no-jargon.sh.
# Format: <relative-path>:<token>   to allow a token in a specific file
#         <token>                    to allow a token globally (use sparingly)
# Lines starting with # are comments. Empty lines ignored.
#
# Add entries with a justification comment ABOVE the entry, e.g.:
#   # 2026-04-27 cradle: legacy Job.wip_account_id grandfathered until cleanup pass
#   packages/esqyma/proto/v1/domain/operation/job/job.proto:wip
